## Agent final message

> Query written to query80.preql and validated successfully. The query uses `raw.all_sales` (multi-channel consolidated model) with ROLLUP for per-outlet, per-channel subtotal, and grand total rows. It filters date range 2000-08-23 to 2000-09-22, items with current_price > 50, promotions with channel_tv = 'N', and only sales with a recorded outlet. Outlet identifiers are built by prefixing the channel's entity text_id with the appropriate label ('store', 'catalog_page', 'web_site'). The query returned 100 rows (limited) covering catalog channel rows (the first channel in sort order). Full dataset (428 rows) includes all three channels plus subtotals and grand total.

